node.content-desc: Customer reviews 4 out of 5 stars 6,058 global ratings

node.text: Customers find the diffuser effective at calming cats, particularly those with anxiety, and appreciate its positive impact on behavior, noting reduced fighting between cats. However, the functionality receives mixed feedback, with some reporting it works well while others say it doesn't work for their cats. Moreover, the product receives mixed reviews for its smell, with some reporting no scent while others complain about a burning plastic odor. Additionally, customers report issues with leakage, with oil dripping onto carpets and walls, and consider the product not worth the money.
